{"tid":2301393,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"李嘉誠及李澤鉅續增持長實股份","createTime":"2020-11-26T09:23:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-27T04:59:15.000Z","uid":21470,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"59ac9f8b93cb6ed561ff48d89894d90e603a4408","tid":2301393,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T09:23:12.000Z","msg":"李嘉誠及李澤鉅續增持長實股份<br />\n<br />\n長和資深顧問李嘉誠及主席李澤鉅持續增持長江實業股份。<br />\n<br />\n兩人透過李嘉誠基金會在上星期五，本星期一至三，以平均價每股43.4733元、42.831元、43.3566元及43.9265元，購入長江實業共70.25萬股。<br />\n<br />\n增持後，李嘉誠持股由35.77%增至35.79%；李澤鉅由35.83%增至35.85%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1562159-20201126.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1562159-20201126.htm&d=ME9RTGLMBg%2Fi%2BHfTLk0cjLktNrE0CDS5yYjP391fFHI%3D&h=6379cc8d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1562159-20201126.htm&h=b4452566\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1562159-20201126.htm</a>"},{"pid":"d66ea2b17d3b3a17ade63f018c9d4df79a81c669","tid":2301393,"uid":333199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T09:24:02.000Z","msg":"係時候入了"},{"pid":"e2ad18e295db2adeea62d72427cfa70271bedd47","tid":2301393,"uid":32782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d66ea2b17d3b3a17ade63f018c9d4df79a81c669","tid":2301393,"uid":333199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T09:24:02.000Z","msg":"係時候入了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T09:26:50.000Z","msg":"年頭到依家兩仔爺都入左好幾次"},{"pid":"072fa53892ae1df936d933b589f5bab2d10532d3","tid":2301393,"uid":60527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T09:40:14.000Z","msg":"佢地入左好多貨<br />\n有冇人解讀下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ef13d10d3ab16a6745cefa39e7d36fefad63dd6","tid":2301393,"uid":18546,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":